text: Mamadzhan Ismailov (27 July 1936 - 7 November 1993) was a Soviet equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:1993 deaths Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tashkent
